---
// Compact sticky crisis banner — visible but not dominant
---

<aside
  class="sticky top-0 z-50 flex min-h-9 w-full flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-x-2 gap-y-0 bg-[var(--emergency-red)] px-3 py-2 text-center text-sm text-white sm:gap-x-3 sm:px-4"
  role="region"
  aria-label="Ayuda inmediata"
>
  <span class="font-medium">
    <span aria-hidden="true">🚨</span> ¿Necesitas ayuda ahora?
  </span>
  <a
    href="tel:8009112000"
    class="font-semibold text-white underline decoration-white/80 underline-offset-2 hover:decoration-white focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-white focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-offset-[var(--emergency-red)]"
    aria-label="Llamar a la línea de crisis 800 911 2000"
  >
    800 911 2000
  </a>
  <span class="hidden sm:inline" aria-hidden="true">·</span>
  <a
    href="tel:911"
    class="text-xs text-white/95 underline decoration-white/60 underline-offset-2 hover:decoration-white sm:text-sm"
    aria-label="Si estás en peligro inmediato llama al 911"
  >
    Si estás en peligro inmediato llama al 911.
  </a>
</aside>
